的PlayStation 5的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/INZSsBU2BZoc0Cyzg69HXHn-5wfk3izywVq-do2cFKw-ZEwIEch4Fxx7FM_iGYjbJlxezCw3_wcxgYHRvEbaBnfsEO84aBd-ktML_t8ksh1rrarg_ZgPy3QcV3itfAgDBC7uncxre7MzwnsErZydHexTDAJGUQU7kco-o0QicIo-ODSSLxV314m-ivxaLuww7hAH7ZWcTqEO3W3oVZdbQAdmzr1E9h42iTJIWU3OZTmd7nTl598W5IAXAzpeY7jmEbacC_yrYT4KOI-zwPTV8jne1h-aDWBAenxOc1OXFJCe-KzhuRkvTiTryfGDM-0mhfpyoBQLe7ApA5Hf5BhsG6Gf1ESxlzn4vxnkV8bJo5kNOBgIwcOhS3eSvA/X3IrT4URIT3aoIq4H6v-6EZ8ENENwIYP/8" target="_blank"&gt;价格&lt;/a&gt;也&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Fl-5JRpPGg3080yKBr2-btFEd0IGBhA_pn3A64O0CbhNyulssbDG8iTOazI5v5qfygTRkRA88XfBch3ef2QWJW7w2TH8r1qLonNgqpPNUzRBfpmEf_BfiHzrvhOPIUSy_Cl61pk8C6hTFGPyUn9sr5c5_-pzfbnFFUpjVl3SQPbt_OUa1EkL3S-0mpUC8wXpbv-wDljbHi5DN2cmPb6g1X7Ixzc-s4iaMjZ7hEqXiQG5vREOxZCwQ2a2WJCYvas75fLs6d2o8PMEpscwdhQIQHiHGtJb8AJbTXL1K7OR-3fui1OKPuAn3lzTqhud294GOJzvf2oMZLVje5GUFCnF4k2ikhnceZ9Rs3B1YayocZAAdhvJOQRBpq5nMQ/UKWRvKPE8Xx8JPyFaPiv8ThsXSanVmR1/8" target="_blank"&gt;可能预览了&lt;/a&gt;美国。该公司引用了“充满挑战的经济环境的背景”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;印度iPhone的增长：&lt;/strong&gt;苹果在过去一年中加大了印度的生产，以至于现在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jQIA89kI4oaSJMwW3uI0nQZS4U9Os-8oNojA6Zm8CfO9S_XfAbzusl41GPaGIcORo_hztB2LrOSDWnzayFy2YTDzJvLbxfdVFII-GMehgYjiMpSc4vFdtdp908PoPtdajPblXeOZAtqyskj4uN7WemDQXLr7usGAHKhPIDr0f_25FOI-oXkECwdZpudHbFGtVosMbUSgIXPd2CH8JSXoQmmrAnY5_31Asx6VpilV2wFtmmv1nRJ4VTTzUIA5hozmhO5O2gcxWEG7aKghElntDH8bENRuQ6REH8Jx2CIFcEAWTSrVm_cuDiz_r4bkfqS2abR_InIk5sU2zKp0hzfL-_lCpboBJi6OfUWII24GivTsiiGMc-sHj6tiGQ/vDlnAV69cj1p9hUCpCyiq3R_c_TTx5Rr/8" target="_blank"&gt;五个iPhone中有一个&lt;/a&gt;来自该国。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;关税收入：&lt;/strong&gt;公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/icHbZM4JZwTDv_c8VJJPaqInYkunelonbxBT6BpO78vjvC2g0jQ