ng style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普说，他仍然打算&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;向手机，计算机和受欢迎的消费电子产品&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yOT6prAimc2ne0UyF8a3uD--uImU1KsXrcUZp-iij3ThtiyhD0PH2kpB3QQzdwVqhZ-tAiqpUBG7Cqe05RyzcOUqf9qDLFLY-mixJWIhRLvdbNx7xmjOkUNRYowIe_FQ_TshEjqvgsIxJmD_P0J9HUyMrcSxpz8-Wyp-LEF3QvmiPpDCaSt_D4hUIRVVzWP5VEcne_oQyQwEqjQnbHRtjkBsKn4vgq_tLuq6aiV4zZgviVmiswmyC8qdRLzmaNhexSweS2eqouTB-myDZqHMLNE8_CBO3nTprR8YymgPxskUnWDlqodn3IVZVnK0xwn9lCE0m6Z40fETZffF3AGr1Dn7e2G6Wr43BAHqCNXLqug2-zVkj0-Ir1IqirU/XUOznD_KqKPnBVIKL6DRcm5FMwqK4P_S/8" title="淡化周末豁免"&gt;征收关税，这将周末的豁免&lt;/a&gt;仅仅是他在重新&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ataDGLzunBsUdXGyqGiW4u4A5sM0m5Ukfv81IZNNl6vbfKGNOT4cMdaXWxRW9v5CJdQRNFYnoJFlIduut-xXYBi1BBNxVXuKxO4dy7UfwNaGG27EJSKkpZnJwiQf0MdPIqRAj418yWCVibbiypC2NfO3kq7NixXzEn0Idofz-bV7z8MbRcg2yKDL2M4CF01H1_GiTPP7IOXwhNMlU2EX570n-Vg-LpIBWSLoKNKaCqbsj2NyRdEFUQwa-5uHySsWL_FROua8KELjv3__VZGXXTUVF0uAKEpIpkZKsXZZfc_LXIYk-7AVq4KuPhsPC_YL-IUeOIKbXYUBqF51p2TI0_j01v1CgN5g8239SykaiHHl2nKjeLCb6jXNi0g/jdjh5KXbjMT7Mu3a8fVlZpciSsZjGLPE/8" title="总体推动"&gt;校准全球贸易的总体&lt;/a&gt;上迈出的一步。美元的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LncRaqbT4XLuJ9b3AQBrZRUoR1ZtjtiEdoYTEgtV2rVw13bFFqJVpAa_gJ5WPgPAHIWdb916-uq0i5tACmkE2lj39rLlk6UbHVoEtWG2UjeroYErjEH1E8vkjOAFkEovwLbVOCF_lBRMovgSDtKOfSXXrG-GpWJeQda7NNOQq4xcXHuDQ4QtvC-l5zIyRQqph-xmtoHCLADYCm1Dbz5Mwvognp6BInuvF6l76ipTDiXGFgCdi6eZmtOSQyECozoIVGxkyoALleXgUN0yA_R_ATlovCdVV-aHQN3pjfTQTzNHHgByjby8jyGIPHZyEaLkZGeTZEmW1ePM6rUYk5Si9i6BsT3CQetrp_KAk3gj2igcM71aFPem0R8wlNs/aGj17dWmxHKkKj5U3BszbWqq75VZdQA1/8" title="衰落恢复了"&gt;下降恢复了&lt;/a&gt;，彭博市值指数在较早地跌至10月以来的最低水平后下降了约0.3％。今年的仪表已经下跌了近6％。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;习近平总统在2025年的第一次海外旅行&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;中，曾在越南，马来西亚和柬埔寨进行， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4gQhV_D2GX6ueCB-WDGXzVBvSoYwAQK2l9mDo0K6ZGe93Eh8bvClsNnfTrLkkSAQXCIc0flikpnUqtHml2UgSrnzBZoWDTHyxGfdEw7QP0KC7IRZQCa3_YW9GfTu7vilJmZ7bpNaMqGajLAjvOYRGOLep7y3P7mC5tReU1aMjd7F33oPjf6TeX-MCfnrmf_4LCZ8DBqzovYC4vMklhoa19s8_YK3Bg7h8EAFpSxbo_4McYef_knKhDITSNju4SueYRLpgZ7WDqEOUArxdm-pduoVGDoYlMC80k8EZ6I5v_VpE8tS49p0QooS5cqnFI2b_kPIz0ppKc_MMnX-y0DMqmVg6XMXIwgVkk45yFc3To1_3_MDlgls9Utz80U/rYo-OJOUn9sac8FQ8Ifq-YaCrfvesaCJ/8" title="是要展示"&gt;目的是展示&lt;/a&gt;中国在东南亚的影响力。特朗普的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9YKv5-zml-TrwYo4NUrpLR78OXgdosvbUOXe13LK-b_S35x7DJp1QcmiLqunRkeTrKiVjzge5wu5S5y4iXJ7ak0Zs1YBkS7wqIRcBXM8IAQtjOlpCvKlL8dnnFdGbFiFtbivOv6LPhrpDjmXL2_3jO12IU4_C12J94rHNDiTx8WXTMRXuvwYvZyJDeue9iqS23o8Ff6dyOiM55zhHMHfnur1Yaw_YAtk7hjblcB49wAtCqrPJsSki_c1gaLsQ4oANNeErLPeDS2rG2iRzqUvpZQmHyfpJCcdFOGinX9vqHpaOwkNRSOTkjgqQ1y4UPFyYV_Alb-K7e7_YBgAQHDH5ZivaQ9lDnlRjl-dOazVD7dPkE0T8zNT9k0Eplk/noRwjljsHphrYaMA18oVywyxBVCitEvc/8" title="关税威胁"&gt;关税威胁&lt;/a&gt;将其变成了阻止该地区领导人以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YQeTcP_d5dYDRSXXCxPQruHzy-WXbRiqcLag9oergcQFbfFBvqQ52lo9lPPd1VW-vHz8ceTlc8l1mRBDKql0oI5HrIm7NMzCgwzZpu521g_XREHBfxl_uCs_TUYmzIx9tsLzmiPtSPTE-SoiJHyCyuBpqmZeOGtlpRvUmjMonh5uE7rltoP49xsZez0MGBZ4Uspf496yYcunb7rG6rUdPBbXaHikuNpGvvmn-qOYCqTNzD05Pkeq8KC8bXSG6X6leA4EDENucEKOcuef187KQEcBjTllGTJetVv49IkYBsOzOGsCuEynz5sACcqybUA-vlKP6SetdA9fWv3bXgq1zK0y_PZQ700wZ5vH8vUf4ZPv9M-CobRDDvV5unk/SVoCnck48UWJNV0BQ0bXPkTDCYwtGxlw/8" title="北京的费用"&gt;北京为代价&lt;/a&gt;削减交易的努力。同时，随着官员们担心跨大西洋关系受到了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/hCOZibMVQWlB8nzsWVESVCTLDHDojnpxNZtK3M0tBMOurRvAu7r9WNRHNVnINKPO-rtQdfo19smDCobE8KpYLzxgDPGZbSRKEQnsBdXjNHpNxJBehJfd_eyDLXqX5piEFvr3Lxu9_izxtCG9NINhBl3RpDTef3D4XZkVUkIuAfqC0pit-jz25vQYuQmPO6zQJ0Er33vavhbEpb1f0Z5l8_3RrUkCIw5b0qGs7ivX3sHmSt6vhCuqodzpi3f9fXwGtfOewOFNT2AT_Tjs8c8ZMy-TniQEI1Fx7anrkss1ULBXiAAzVc2VryDhqE6QqGtWN9jRTxmv001DWRKvbMKnTctiiJA26MuBTchVc5myNwqL9j_OXERj8MqfC60/hbyg1iW-KTcuHzRbqT57hAejsz8zC875/8" title="不可逆转地损坏"&gt;不可逆转的损害&lt;/a&gt;，欧盟正在争取贸易协议，以使贸易协议脱离美国。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;厄瓜多尔&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;的&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;选举机构宣布&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;总统丹尼尔·诺贝亚（Daniel Noboa）是昨天的径流投票的获胜者，在他接任临时领导人的16个月后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/slVAMpQeivhrOTuW5ubWee1FVA0Q0dIkjXtY1Mc0v_Ej72l0Ldgwr-5LP92NKXMs-zQwocu5EBrL89PvrxCANRRWkYPLVwof-J8jMOkDypft-UZI8of5DTQox02ag-x1q3kGEQZVtZWzFVk6GN6chqUagEBT9-YygK6JW4mxRR-71pZfMI_Q4pDd1CW6vQv9yzJZrdN21EGCa2LNh77f_8kQqleP3eKoH_HZ6scHp6nnPnkeTaAmQjwQRWbXQVslg8PXneN0bOlLIgY8PW-fP_bwGJrkXUWxaL8HvlC833LqAEFPNgRon-CXUm4s0fte7pCG_I6bcU7zr1Cmp47DDoQSx95PCchWq5AEQxMbY7ygjOrMWPd8Bviu3Go/7HEQdkoEIeDg_ndrsOM29x0IBDhFks9-/8"&gt;他给了他更多的时间&lt;/a&gt;来解决拉丁美洲国家的毒品帮派和全国性停电的地方问题。虽然总统候选人路易莎·冈萨雷斯（LuisaGonzález）拒绝承认，但Noboa的领导表明，他现在将有一个完整的期限，并试图控制可卡因有联系的暴力和经济动荡。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;阿根廷在该国创纪录的金融救助案倒塌仅六年后，获得了一项200亿美元的国际货币基金计划，开始拆除&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;外交交换控制。这是华盛顿IMF在过去的七十年中即将救出阿根廷的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XHD3mAEA78BVsinh_xVi2JPyDncxO576r_N8wZzXfPLdCRLqFPTC-3H9-Vyg7JygkAH3H8qpul4K5dycY-1IpHexof06piHzdqKltvhno7q1EzJKnR4KP3ErKoKvotl_TxVvRc9dQEtGSlmQnpHCSGUJ4QpBIM4wNBy4t77mmJs-UFj5cIrWOd_aYFigI2wrBjl_u-5o0iKWjnjuOqve2y-MVxCwzUmJiHpaEShLFF6aqe3xNmFqYgGoSPeCkaMJo0reUIJnXsU9002CzTk-3GYwUeaQNoS7z_QXSgN692BQ3zyxeM2E0qa6tPYgZl3u6XAmtu6cpEpxHfdT5dP_-ykcil-EyE4kRTWVMN5lkR3giksKHo0GsBgo8Cw/pWAzBz2Tn0vWZQeV0Hz3SGtWdcAnAa13/8"&gt;第23次&lt;/a&gt;，其巨大的区别是，陷入困境的南美国家的经济现在在自由主义者总统贾维尔·米利（Javier Milei）的领导下。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;伊朗和美国表示，&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;自从特朗普返回以来&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;，他们就德黑兰的核计划进行了首次正式谈判&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dWbZl2Kdf3HZtD9T_ycMAEkTRzKUeo9RMIXWCnQQ2Yeieksh0Dz9TIl2FmEc28h2b7JWd3tcplhsxmMPZozow7-XQbmlSDeFHp_ZPkoE3x76CcZTbTwVKwHyX8HwOuY8Pvzw7-diSfA91sUPHTLztQAS6G50_e6Ar_UvtJCnFXU8fYHcfzZGuWuStuWNH0pIhMAMbhG3XxQi-NCoJ8fMTUwqqZJQ68VIifCIWZRELL4QPM4kYr6o9dyOJD94ArWmR6NnoTlcueH2rQYDqX7ctA8GbhIdT3J4J0mGHEt6FKJ9_nLDE3VVvV7IWAQzKH4YohnjRxknHbN7tdl4eJEGadIxb-NKU-vtqvNcn4pczFIy6cS25ZGaz5fxBM4/oNvZ4Xrz5548T7fWIs9axow4U-MnkIN3/8" title="建设性"&gt;，&lt;/a&gt;并同意在一周内再次在罗马见面。伊朗外交大臣阿巴斯·阿拉格奇（Abbas Araghchi）和美国特使维特科夫（Witkoff）在谈判后短暂地见面并发表了讲话，这是自2022年以来的首次顶级讨论，标志着解决了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mZxHXHXrqVf2m69nQ7zAfx-NI6RK0e-gvA44UBqrJSf5493nuQlmFBdadJ_3C22T-wX-Skrd6HyCbt9qlRlRuIc1FixqW58ePDZ6y9YgJws431czaC-pyJr8rT0Bvu8d50teYItNbUZpGqijpR59mdDeynD_6nPjCpzpIiID4pc_v1oHrEaruqNSD-3ZtHjcsh6a1q3Ic_ujPh6A2t2h33PHgltJS6phBwaV27K_SH0tSH3hoMVh7Ms8jegTmjQgGgsFGC8BGVpYN8_K27xqfE0PLJRmJMmBjOR7d_7jstWK79osBPlASzg6ZMlvPjcKT6HpeRaDe7w99-WmB2Dq3a-bSG9Qf7eB2BonK5aMlWikmJjARYDqD_Utdeo/aGTz_teOLnY09Lhf3z9jcQ7-F3Qs_r4T/8" title="多年对峙"&gt;多年僵持的&lt;/a&gt;重新努力。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIh3dm3egTb0/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIh3dm3egTb0/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rdzXYHF0qaPukAeopXMcMs00fQ_Q7Xnp8tCUfh6GWLoiCPUkwHfpC96MZB_z-SjooIziD7susuYRweLZYNx0t33UGYPjIEaQqTxujcoNgIXDUcVh3hUgZWkTGE-YZTzYeRum49Jz_C-Foe1bMPSM3VvCUCNiHa_knBd95r3IMDyJeBusXjro9O9LJD65ILuTXRnzjCrGCq07Q5s9znF6TUA1044siwOo4eUkVWe5YbElp9ZduqMklhGV42KqOMA-HTB2523FeYzN_SF7PHWaM1cnXYfduPrOQbxy4ONFDwb65x32n77ZpjKhwUTDvwdbHD42Hotovg83ps9ca2GH1hRILSO-Rtb1K4XieHGcjrkVtiByCIOTH_G3RQ4/ou3aD5mjztJf9eAcB60drInchJ7KBy1S/8" title="报告"&gt;报纸的报告&lt;/a&gt;， &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;南非最大的政党&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;非洲人国民大会将退缩，以增加在国家统一政府内部和外部的政党之后增加增值税的计划。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;加蓬的军事领导人布里斯·奥利吉·恩吉玛（Brice Oligui Nguema）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;巩固了他的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HriEV7yoG4vhpbItyC7wp3ETkKJoAteW9Wt43WBqRdZ3ICokiTrWFUmmJhPTcbYGRlOEcvN9hR5nSol0IHbQKLaEpv9bqy1BxYLSVwiUtkuWNfmCov9WsH3AFz5i0tuTILFNLxokfJ1DaLqGsl_0CXL5OsFLoBdP082AEDfaJPeakW35x0p35NxiRO_kMi3-M5sRdoaToOrjFBdiSH4o7P8-jRHemDAa9UBfczxCpk7UfEjJ_M0dvL37GTH2j8_t44ZVWc7YFiFmmNptE0Ij4Y1zl0vxkewn3AdXrQfg13MddL6AxZ6WM1oxn2zoX2fciaaXHA-xZSDbI-wOlGWpyWzQ9LEJo9zmvaP7JnR5ZHvE_W7gcfhNeCXTpE8/Sn3DgzJQhxRYuD7_-t7IviJhHcRFJQkh/8" title="抓住力量"&gt;权力&lt;/a&gt;，自两年前推翻政府以来，他赢得了该国的第一次总统大选。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https